BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS OF EVERGLADES DRAINAGE DISTRICT, a public quasi-corporation, v. DADE COUNTY, a Political Subdivision of the State of Florida, et al. 23 So. (2nd) 385

June Term, 1945

September 28, 1945 Special Division B Willard. Utley, for appellant. Hudson & Cason and Park H. Campbell, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The record and the briefs in this cause have been examined and we find no reversible error. The judgment appealed from is therefore affirmed.

Affirmed.

TERRELL, BROWN, THOMAS and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
